column16: Matt Duffy flies out to right fielder Matt Kemp.
Joe Panik grounds into a force out, third baseman Brett Wallace to second baseman Adam Rosales.   Madison Bumgarner to 3rd.    Denard Span out at 2nd.    Joe Panik to 1st.
Denard Span singles on a ground ball to center fielder Travis Jankowski, deflected by pitcher Tayron Guerrero.   Madison Bumgarner to 2nd.
Angel Pagan flies out to left fielder Melvin Upton Jr.

Giants challenged (tag play), call on the field was upheld: Brandon Crawford doubles (9) on a line drive to right fielder Matt Kemp.   Hunter Pence scores.  Brandon Crawford out at 3rd on the throw, right fielder Matt Kemp to second baseman Adam Rosales to catcher Derek Norris to third baseman Brett Wallace.
Hunter Pence singles on a ground ball to left fielder Melvin Upton Jr.
Brandon Belt grounds out, third baseman Brett Wallace to first baseman Wil Myers.
Buster Posey flies out to right fielder Matt Kemp.
